item.title: CVE-2019-0330|2024-08-04T17:44:16.508Z -- sap%20se -- sap%20diagnostic%20agent%20%28lm-service%29
item.description: The OS Command Plugin in the transaction GPA_ADMIN and the OSCommand Console of SAP Diagnostic Agent (LM-Service), version 7.2, allow an attacker to inject code that can be executed by the application. An attacker could thereby control the behavior of the application.
